name: Agog 17 Sky Scribble
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D scribble sculpture lines and loop. One of my favorite scribbles in the Agog VR world. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
